public class MathMLCompiler
extends Object

compile

public ASTNodeValue compile(String name)
Description copied from interface: ASTNodeCompiler
A compiler will also have to deal with a name. The meaning of this can be various. For instance, the name may refer to a Species in the system. In case of numerical computation, the ASTNodeCompiler must create an ASTNodeValue representing the current value of this Species.
